## Visual Studio / .NET build output and user-specific files.
## Trimmed from the full https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/VisualStudio.gitignore

# Build output
bin/
obj/
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/

# User-specific / IDE files
*.user
*.suo
*.userprefs

# Signing material — never commit keystores or passwords
*.keystore
*.keystore~
*.jks
# Local signing config (copy signing.props.template -> signing.props and fill in)
EsbImuReceiverToLanAndroid/signing.props
